1
00:01:29,810 --> 00:01:33,090
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:36,240
[Episode 3]

3
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:44,810
Is it done?

4
00:01:45,330 --> 00:01:46,759
Along with the two attendants,

5
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:48,620
they've been disposed of as well.

6
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:51,720
It's his own arrogance to blame.

7
00:01:51,740 --> 00:01:53,479
He didn't even know who he offended.

8
00:01:53,479 --> 00:01:55,780
But he was our guest after all.

9
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,860
What if someone looks into it?

10
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:00,120
Don't worry.

11
00:02:01,020 --> 00:02:02,700
The one who wanted him dead

12
00:02:02,730 --> 00:02:03,810
will handle it.

13
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:07,430
Where did you go

14
00:02:08,530 --> 00:02:10,259
during tonight's death match?

15
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,680
I saw the death match was about to fail,

16
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,300
so I planned to step in myself.

17
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:17,329
Unexpectedly,

18
00:02:17,350 --> 00:02:18,510
I was still too late,

19
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:20,250
and accidentally let those three

20
00:02:20,250 --> 00:02:21,450
slip through by luck.

21
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:26,140
It doesn't matter.

22
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,320
Even if

23
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:28,550
they escape this level,

24
00:02:28,550 --> 00:02:30,210
they will die sooner or later.

25
00:02:30,820 --> 00:02:32,200
But Wujiu,

26
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:33,640
I have to remind you:

27
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,079
if I find out

28
00:02:35,079 --> 00:02:36,200
that it was you

29
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:39,000
who broke the rules of Lingya Tower,

30
00:02:40,540 --> 00:02:42,340
I will absolutely show no mercy.

31
00:02:46,530 --> 00:02:47,680
We've had our fun

32
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:49,270
and the vermin have been eliminated.

33
00:02:49,270 --> 00:02:50,630
Send those three

34
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,260
up to the next level.

35
00:02:52,730 --> 00:02:53,410
Yes.

36
00:03:11,090 --> 00:03:14,780
[Second Level: Elite Academy]

37
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:50,400
Where is this?

38
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:54,170
Are we out of Lingya Tower?

39
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,680
Is this yours?

40
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:07,490
Who told you to touch it?

41
00:04:07,850 --> 00:04:08,680
I didn't.

42
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,400
I didn't know it was yours.

43
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,090
I just picked it up.

44
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,030
If you ever touch my things again,

45
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:14,560
I'll chop your hands off, got it?

46
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,160
How can you be so unreasonable?

47
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:18,440
-She meant well.
-I don't need it.

48
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,800
Can you two stop

49
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,870
being so hypocritical here?

50
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:21,950
What is this place?

51
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,080
Lingya Tower.

52
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,560
You know exactly
what kind of people you are,

53
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,820
and how you got in here.

54
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:27,530
Don't play dumb.

55
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,280
In Lingya Tower,

56
00:04:30,550 --> 00:04:31,440
it's either kill

57
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,280
or be killed.

58
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:33,680
Don't give me that sisterhood nonsense

59
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,080
or your scheming tricks.

60
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,000
Right.

61
00:04:38,930 --> 00:04:40,560
There are no good people in this tower.

62
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,690
They are all beasts.

63
00:04:43,020 --> 00:04:44,170
But an extra ally

64
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:46,250
is better than an extra enemy, right?

65
00:04:46,530 --> 00:04:48,250
Who knows, maybe when you die one day,

66
00:04:48,250 --> 00:04:50,180
someone might be there to bury you.

67
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,520
How kind of you.

68
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:03,020
Speak no evil.

69
00:05:16,730 --> 00:05:19,150
[The Voice-keeper of the Second Level:
Qin Yuren]

70
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:18,570
I am the voice-keeper here.

71
00:05:18,590 --> 00:05:19,890
Qin Yuren.

72
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,680
You can call me Madam Qin.

73
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:26,520
Your mother was poisoned
by Lingya Tower's toxin.

74
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:28,920
I can only temporarily contain its spread.

75
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:33,840
Master,

76
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,159
what is this?

77
00:05:38,490 --> 00:05:39,680
The Guiding Ring.

78
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,159
Welcome to the death match

79
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:45,120
on the second level of Lingya Tower.

80
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,280
Death match?

81
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,320
It's starting so soon?

82
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:50,040
Our Elite School

83
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:52,020
uses exams as death matches.

84
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,400
Those with excellent grades

85
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:55,280
can be promoted to the upper level.

86
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,890
The rest who fail,

87
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:59,520
as long as they're willing
to remain my students,

88
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:01,280
can stay here indefinitely.

89
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,520
That sounds

90
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:07,650
a million times better
than the lower level, doesn't it?

91
00:06:21,570 --> 00:06:22,330
This...

92
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,750
This place is so nice!

93
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:29,160
Why don't we just stay here?

94
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:31,420
Then we don't have to
take part in any death matches.

95
00:06:31,420 --> 00:06:32,840
Stay if you want.

96
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,280
Looking at all these books

97
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:36,140
just gives me a massive headache.

98
00:06:36,180 --> 00:06:37,450
If we stay here,

99
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,520
without participating in the death match

100
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:41,120
or attending these classes,

101
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,740
what will happen to us?

102
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:46,000
If someone always fails to learn,

103
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,930
they're definitely a bad student.

104
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,280
When such a hard-won opportunity

105
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:51,640
isn't cherished,

106
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,640
then the only option is

107
00:06:55,370 --> 00:06:56,510
to kill them.

108
00:07:05,540 --> 00:07:07,700
[First Meeting]

109
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:31,240
My mother made this rabbit meat
especially for you.

110
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:35,010
Can I be your apprentice?

111
00:07:36,470 --> 00:07:38,080
I like rabbit meat too.

112
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:40,020
Can you teach me how to catch them?

113
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:47,340
Look, my braiding isn't that bad, right?

114
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:50,380
Master.

115
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:52,430
When will you start teaching me?

116
00:07:52,740 --> 00:07:55,200
When did I agree
to take you as my apprentice?

117
00:07:55,860 --> 00:07:57,940
For the sake of me combing your hair,

118
00:07:57,970 --> 00:07:59,700
won't you consider it, Master?

119
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,880
I've never taken an apprentice.

120
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:02,640
I don't know how to teach.

121
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:04,850
I've never had a master either.

122
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:07,250
We can just look out for each other.

123
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,010
I'll think about it.

124
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,990
I'll take that as a yes.

125
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,960
Let's pinky swear on it.

126
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:15,840
No backing out.

127
00:08:15,990 --> 00:08:19,920
Do you know how much pain and suffering
it takes to master these skills?

128
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,290
Look, Master!

